text: So Salem had a tantrum this morning. I stayed the night at my boyfriend’s house and came home to get ready and she started meowing hysterically then started throwing herself on the floor. It was hilarious b/c when she would throw herself down it would push the meow out and make it like a hmmphh..
Musashi also does this, especially when it's hot
I wish I would have caught it on video but I was running around getting ready while she was falling apart on the floor hahahahahah
I get the hmmphh a lot from my cats
